data.description: This 2-story home is located just off of the Powers corridor making it close to shopping, dining, entertainment, and military bases.  Covered front porch,  It offers lofted ceilings with a bright and open floor plan. The Living Room features a double sided gas fireplace with wood floors that continue throughout the main level.  The Dining Room has a walk-out to the backyard patio and new 12x18 deck. The Kitchen features plenty of natural light, also walks out to the patio, a pantry, and plenty of cabinet space.  The laundry area is also on the main level as well as a guest bathroom. The upper area features a large loft/flex room with built-in bookcases . The large Master Bedroom has a private full Bath and walk-in closet. There are 2 additional Bedrooms, 1 has a walk-in closet, and a full Bath on the upper level as well.   Needs some TLC but that is reflected in the price. Time to make it your own!
